# TODO: mutual recursion with match body — second binding (is_odd) gets
# threaded through a runtime continuation instead of landing as a direct
# LetFn sibling like ping/pong. Expected output below is the blessed
# (current) shape, which is reasonable per-se — but downstream wasm
# collect misses one of the hoisted fns. Fix likely in wasm collect
# traversal; keep this snapshot to detect if lifting shape shifts.
